      • compare

        private int compare(E left,
                    E right)
        Compare two items using either a Comparator object’s compare method or their natural ordering using method compareTo. pre: If comparator is null, left and right implement Comparable.
        Parameters:
        left - One item
        right - The other item
        Returns:
        Negative int if left less than right, 0 if left equals right, positive int if left greater than right
        Throws:
        java.lang.ClassCastException - if items are not Comparable
